- Example project setups: use projects array in config to run multiple test environments; use environment: 'node' for pure node tests.
- Assertion usage: import { test, expect } from 'vitest'; expect(actual).toBe(expected) and other matchers supported.
- Test selection and focused tests: use test.only for single test; use --threads=1 or --run for single-run CI.

